Weekly performance metrics must be distributed to management by end-of-business Monday.
Monthly trend analysis must be completed by the 5th of the following month.

#Compliance and Data Privacy
#Regulatory Adherence
100% of orders involving personal or sensitive data must undergo privacy impact assessment.
All data transfers must comply with applicable regional data protection regulations.
Compliance audits must be conducted quarterly with remediation of findings within 15business days.

